	<p style="padding-left: 30px;">B. Backups. For its own operational efficiencies and purposes, Hosting Account Setup from time to time backs up data on its servers, but is under no obligation or duty to Subscriber to do so under these Terms. IT IS SOLELY SUBSCRIBER&#8217;S DUTY AND RESPONSIBILITY TO BACKUP SUBSCRIBER&#8217;S FILES AND DATA ON Hosting Account Setup SERVERS, AND under no circumstance will Hosting Account Setup be liable to anyone FOR DAMAGES OF ANY KIND under any legal theory for loss of Subscriber FILES AND/or data on any Hosting Account Setup server. Hosting Account Setup will not attempt to back up accounts that exceed 50,000 files or 30 Gigs of space for any reason.<br />
	<p style="padding-left: 30px;">C. Monitoring and Disclosures. All activities occurring on, in, and/or via the Services or any website hosted by Hosting Account Setup may be monitored, recorded, and examined by any authorized person, including as well law enforcement. In general, Hosting Account Setup does not monitor its Subscribers&#8217; websites or activities to determine whether they are in compliance with these Terms. However, when and if Hosting Account Setup becomes aware of any violation of these Terms, Hosting Account Setup may take any lawful action, and in the event of illegal activity, will take action, to stop or correct such violation, including, but not limited to, shutting down a website, denying access to the Services or to the Internet via Hosting Account Setup, and/or removing non-complying information. In addition, Hosting Account Setup may take any lawful action against a Subscriber or a Subscriber, patron, customer, invitee, visitor, or guest of such Subscriber because of the activities of such Subscriber, patron, customer, invitee, visitor, or guest. Hosting Account Setup reserves the right to take any such action even though such action may affect other Subscribers, patrons, customers, invitees, visitors, or guests of the Subscriber. Hosting Account Setup may disclose any information in its possession, including, without limitation, information about Subscribers, internet transmissions and website activity in order to comply with a court order, subpoena, summons, discovery request, warrant, statute, regulation, governmental request, or other legal process to protect Hosting Account Setup or others from harm, and/or to ensure the proper operation of the Services. Hosting Account Setup.com has no obligation to notify any person, including the Subscriber about whom information is sought, that Hosting Account Setup has provided the information.<br />
	<p style="padding-left: 30px;">D. Accurate Account Information. Subscriber must continually update and keep accurate and current Subscriber&#8217;s contact information stored and saved on Hosting Account Setup in order to avoid termination of Subscriber&#8217;s Hosting Account Setup account(s).<br />
	<p style="padding-left: 30px;">E. Duty to Notify Hosting Account Setup of Breach. If Subscriber discovers anyone on the Hosting Account Setup system violating any of these Terms or notices anything suspicious from the Hosting Account Setup network, Subscriber agrees to report the violation or suspicious activity to support@AllPhase.com for investigation. Hosting Account Setup reserves the right to and will immediately terminate any account which Hosting Account Setup concludes to be in violation of any of these Terms.<br />
	<p style="padding-left: 30px;">F. Reservation of Rights. Hosting Account Setup reserves the right to refuse or to cancel service to any prospective Subscriber or existing Subscriber for any lawful reason at any time during Subscriber&#8217;s hosting term with Hosting Account Setup.<br />
	<p style="padding-left: 30px;">G. Severability. These Terms are binding upon Hosting Account Setup, all existing and prospective Subscribers, and upon the assigns, heirs, and successors of each. If any provision of these Terms is held by any court of competent jurisdiction to be invalid or otherwise unenforceable, the rest of these Terms shall, nevertheless, continue to be valid and in full force and effect, to the extent said remaining Terms are then otherwise consistent with the original intent of the Terms of Service.<br />
	<p style="padding-left: 30px;">H. Governing Law. These Terms shall be governed by the laws of the State of Ohio without reference to conflict of law principles. The United Nations Convention on the International Sale of Goods shall not apply and is hereby expressly excluded. By subscribing to or using any of the Services of Hosting Account Setup, Subscriber agrees that all disputes, if any, involving Hosting Account Setup shall be subject exclusively to the jurisdiction of the State and Federal Courts within the State of Ohio; provided, further, that all action brought against Hosting Account Setup in State Court must be brought in Franklin County, Ohio and, if in Federal Court, in Franklin County, Ohio. Subscriber hereby agrees that it is subject to the in personam jurisdiction of said courts for all purposes in connection with these Terms and/or in connection with any claim or dispute involving Hosting Account Setup. Subscriber hereby waives any and all objections that it has or might have, known or unknown, whether under Ohio&#8217;s long arm statute or otherwise, to the existence of said in personam jurisdiction. Subscriber agrees that it has no right to and shall not file or otherwise bring a lawsuit against Hosting Account Setup outside the State of Ohio; and, that Subscriber, if involved before a court in a lawsuit outside of the State of Ohio, shall be deemed to support and to stipulate to a motion made by Hosting Account Setup to dismiss said lawsuit with respect to Hosting Account Setup.<br />
